  {exe} serve --port 8888\n\
  {exe} --mock-quota \"free::/free/moonshotai/kimi-k2;req=100;tok=50000;free\"\n\
  {exe} --model /free/moonshotai/kimi-k2 --env OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...\n\
\n\
Supported binary names (argv[0]):\n\
  ollama          - Standard Ollama CLI compatibility\n\
  ollama_emulator - Full emulator name\n\
  modelmux        - Model muxer alias\n\
  agent8888       - 888agent alias"
